#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/20.users/groups_and_permissions.mdx:263
#, no-wrap
msgid "Each group can use mail aliases, but their configuration is only available from the CLI so far. For example, the `admins` group is configured with aliases such as `admins@domain.tld`, `root@domain.tld` ... : mail sent to these addresses will be dispatched to all members of the `admins` group.\n"
